attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Create Cisco IOS XR 7.0.1 telemetry model-driven configuration for VRF operational monitoring (VRF state and route-targets). Use gRPC with no TLS. Telemetry server 192.0.2.117 port 57500. Choose relevant sensor-paths."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group VRF-OPER-MONITOR
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-rsi-oper:vrfs/vrf/state
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-rsi-oper:vrfs/vrf/route-targets/route-target
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 192.0.2.117
    port 57500
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-VRF-OPER-MONITOR
  sensor-group-id VRF-OPER-MONITOR sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
